<BaseLayout title="About | Shingai Thornton">
  <article class="prose">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-8">About</h1>
    <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-6">
      <p>
        I'm Shingai Thornton, a systems scientist interested in how complex adaptive systems
        emerge, evolve, and interact. My research bridges network science, cryptoeconomics,
        and political economy.
      </p>
      <p>
        Currently pursuing graduate work in systems science, with a focus on interstate
        commerce networks and economic complexity. I'm particularly interested in how
        formal methods from systems theory can illuminate the structure and dynamics
        of socio-technical systems.
      </p>
    </div>
